Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:16.02,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,恳请大家 施与悲悯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:18.97,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我是一个来自贫穷农村 地位低下的农民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.87,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我失去了双亲 现在是一个孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:26.92,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,只有依靠大家的悲悯 才能生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:32.43,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,如果大家看到我这副样子 略感同情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:36.43,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,恳请大家 施与我一些零钱 免受饥饿之苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:56.28,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,今天才赚了六便士 你在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:01.44,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,你以为是谁在养着你这样肮脏的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:03.74,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,我可不是做慈善的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.97,italics screener,Wis Narrator,0,0,0,,虽然现在的生活很艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:28.78,italics screener,Wis Narrator,0,0,0,,但也不全是不幸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.93,italics screener,Wis Narrator,0,0,0,,在阁楼的最里面 有一扇窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:36.93,italics screener,Wis Narrator,0,0,0,,如果我在午夜之后敲三下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.49,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.50,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:45.72,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.23,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我在这 威斯媞莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:54.51,italics screener,Wis Narrator,0,0,0,,这就是 我与某个恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:57.54,italics screener,Wis narrator,0,0,0,,秘密相见的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:06.02,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\fs57\bord0\shad0\pos(771,915)\fad(980,1)}第一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:12.28,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯 你今晚也来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.01,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.84,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,那 今天也—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:16.01,top screener,Father,0,0,0,,喂 臭女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.20,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,你还醒着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.28,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.96,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,妈的 我告诉过你明天又要早起的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:26.16,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,如果又像今天一样没赚到钱 我就再揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:28.10,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.35,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,呀嘞呀嘞 虽然由我这个恶魔来说有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:39.96,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,但让孤儿在街上乞讨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.89,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,还能叫神父吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:46.80,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,神父大人照顾了我 而且才不是乞讨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:53.07,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,街上听了我故事的人 都感动地施与我钱财
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:56.77,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,这是合理收入 我这是在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.07,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,嘛 也能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.08,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,自那以来 已经一个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.18,flashback italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,果然还是不存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.52,flashback italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,能看见我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.96,flashback italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,如果没有人承认你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.69,flashback italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,那和不存在也没区别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:26.00,flashback italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这不死的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.64,flashback italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,今后都还得活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:31.46,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,恳请大家 施与悲悯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:37.11,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,如果大家看到我这副样子 略感同情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.10,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,恳请大家 施与我一些零钱 免受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.10,flashbacktop screener,Passerby,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:51.25,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,真可怜啊 真是看着都让人心痛的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:55.75,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,难道你打算直到死都做这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.62,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,不会对活着厌倦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:04.94,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,对着看不见我 听不见我的人揪心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.49,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我到底还是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:17.04,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,等等 难道你能看见我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.93,flashback screener,Father,0,0,0,,你傻站在那干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.66,flashback screener,Father,0,0,0,,过来 我们要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.54,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,骗人的吧 你是早上的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.56,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,你跟踪我到这的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:50.30,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,果然 你能看见我这样的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.30,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,是的 自我出生以来就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:00.05,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,你是来带走我的灵魂的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.04,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,不 我只是对能看见我的人类好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.79,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.32,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:14.37,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,那么 你能在我睡着前 给我讲故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.45,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.17,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,欸 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:24.49,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我感觉 如果今晚就这样睡着 不会有什么好梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.88,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.55,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,今天要讲的是什么故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.20,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,你又想听睡前故事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.85,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,如果明天因为起不来被揍 我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:44.49,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛 唯独这个我一直很期盼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:49.73,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我想听你的故事 感受旅行的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:59.33,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,那就 200年前 不对 应该是300年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.53,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,你记不清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:07.13,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这个故事 关于我在这个伦敦 看了莎士比亚的戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.31,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,嘁 就这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.07,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,别放下警惕 斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:04.06,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,我也没要你来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.84,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,再怎么说 我也是你的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.44,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,根据总部的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:15.16,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,伦敦市内被目击的是相当高阶的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:17.69,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,不是这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.11,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,继续找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.70,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,哇 太有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:28.38,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,莎士比亚 我没想到故事能这么有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.33,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,如果能在剧场看一定更棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.66,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,也没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.85,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我看了所有有名的戏剧 全都一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.92,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,对不起它们的名气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:46.20,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯 你肯定没有朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.61,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,哈 你在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.35,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,而且也没那么多能看见我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.97,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:56.04,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,活了这么久 你却不了解人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:57.36,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,很讽刺哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.39,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这绝不可能 虽然只是短时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.06,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我可以变为人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.01,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.55,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这种形态 其他人类也能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:13.26,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,所以 并不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.52,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我没有机会和人类交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:20.65,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,但是这很费神 用着很疲劳 所以我并不常用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.13,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:29.03,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,如果让发情的女人看见这种形态 会引起慌乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.50,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.50,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:41.19,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,怎么了 我刚刚说的有什么好笑的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.04,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:47.54,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,如果那都不懂的话 你还有的要学呢 玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.25,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.87,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,那么 我还会再来点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.00,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:58.42,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯 我真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:03.30,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,遇见你后 我开始能期待明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:10.13,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我小时候 一直不喜欢我这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:15.14,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,因为能看见别人看不见的东西 别人都畏惧我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.78,flashbacktop screener,Child 1,0,0,0,,臭怪物 滚远点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:17.95,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,好事一件没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.96,flashbacktop screener,Child 2,0,0,0,,太哈人了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:22.82,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,但是 现在这双能看见你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.80,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我已经视为宝物了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:36.89,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:40.37,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,她不过碰巧是个能看见我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:44.58,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,哪儿都能看见的不幸小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:49.88,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,为什么 我会不断去见她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.41,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,臭女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.96,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,我们终于找到愿意买你的买家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.90,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,买家 欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:05.42,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,真傻啊你 你真以为乞讨就够养你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.78,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,那不过是在展示商品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:12.80,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,我的任务是领养孤儿 稍加打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:15.80,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,再把他们卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.77,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,你很幸运 长得格外漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:24.93,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,因此你能被有领地的贵族买走 而不是进入妓院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:29.80,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,你之后也许能过上不错的生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.61,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,明天交付
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.49,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,在那之前 好好享受最后的晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.33,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这样 他果然是人贩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.29,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,那时也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:56.48,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我的哥哥 在我小时候 就是那样被带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:02.34,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,起初 我以为他会被带去宅邸做仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.01,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,但自那以后 他再杳无音信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:11.09,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,之后才知道 没有人知道有那样的宅邸存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:17.00,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我们都被骗了 之后要一直遭受折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.37,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,恳请你 把我带离这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.26,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.38,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.13,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这会违背我们恶魔所遵守的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:32.78,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,如果我们无代价救一个人 我们的身体会抗拒 最终化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.91,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我们就是这样的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:39.88,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.26,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,请带走我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:53.30,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我知道 恶魔可以用人类的灵魂 或对他们来说珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.89,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,来实现人类的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:00.34,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我以前认为 用生命实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.22,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.92,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,但如果是被你夺去灵魂 我能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:11.21,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,哥哥走后 对我来说重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.07,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,除了你 别无他人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:18.95,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,你知道为什么恶魔要灵魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:24.24,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,因为他能用所夺取的 延长自己的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.63,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,但我已是不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.00,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,再夺取灵魂也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.56,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,不如说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:37.07,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我早就受够不老不死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.44,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,这样 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:50.02,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,你已经什么都不再需要了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:13.97,flashback italics screener,Wis,0,0,0,,呐 玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.99,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,你为什么来到伦敦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.82,flashback screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 可能是为了缓解无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.12,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,这样 那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.99,flashback screener,Wis,0,0,0,,你现在有真的感到快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.51,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,打开 我叫你打开啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:37.66,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,斯诺 这里再怎么说也是教会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.25,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,作为骑士团的一员 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.40,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,我才不管那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.64,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,剑术士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:50.94,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,不停下的话 我们就从你的工资里扣除门的修缮费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:51.65,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.15,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,唯独这个别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:59.64,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,你们谁啊 这可是神圣的教会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.30,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:03.53,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,你不是在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.39,main screener,Subordinate,0,0,0,,我买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.65,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.54,main screener,Subordinate,0,0,0,,喂 快向主人问候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.71,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.04,main screener,Subordinate,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.77,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,没事的 没有什么好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.56,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,来吧 威斯媞莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.29,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,从今天起 你就是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.79,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,放松点 把这当成自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.35,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.81,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,这就是你的寝室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.11,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,感谢主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.57,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:15:00.68,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,我们追踪恶魔的踪迹到这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:02.25,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,你有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.58,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,我 我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:11.34,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,我们知道你真正所干的勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.83,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,就算毁了也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.23,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,等等等等 我说 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.33,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,恶魔我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:24.23,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,但有一个经常在夜晚自言自语的银发少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.16,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,银发 这个女孩在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:31.00,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,我把他卖给了有钱的地主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:37.26,main screener,Father,0,0,0,,听说 他是一个喜欢折磨儿童的变态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.57,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,你这个人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:42.96,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,竹波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.66,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,不好意思 我要做的事已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.96,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,喂 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.36,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,刚刚那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.85,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,测量器爆表了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.56,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.96,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:05.91,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,我只是想治愈你那贫穷不幸的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.69,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:15.12,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,看起来是个难缠的货呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.14,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,哪可能跑得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.02,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,该放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.81,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,你不可能逃出这个宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.30,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,现在是愉悦时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.34,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.83,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,你这家伙谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.82,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,按照你们人类的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.32,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,有钱就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.34,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,那个女孩我买下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.79,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:11.34,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,我可从没见过这么好的货色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.35,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,你出多少 我都不会给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.10,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.11,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,抗拒反应来得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.09,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,他怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:28.91,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.10,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,你tm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.49,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:47.61,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我本以为我对一切都失去了兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:52.24,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这个世界再也没有值得去看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.12,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:59.88,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,唯独与你一起的夜晚 能让我不再无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:06.39,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,那真不错 我很久没有感受过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:07.72,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,威斯媞莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.31,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我本以为我早已放弃了期盼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:18.41,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,但看起来 我想有与你携手共进的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.28,main screener,Demon,0,0,0,,真是吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.67,italics screener,Wis,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:35.68,italics screener,Wis,0,0,0,,那个人和恶魔签订契约了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.37,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:02.48,main screener,Demon,0,0,0,,你还没签订契约呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.62,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:08.42,main screener,Demon,0,0,0,,破坏了规则 你还以为能打败我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.71,italics screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,要撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.63,main screener,Demon,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.14,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯 我们签订契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:30.85,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,我最珍惜的 这双能看见你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.39,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,足以支付代价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.89,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,请呆在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.55,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,玛尔巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.02,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,这个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:57.97,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,不是像你这种肮脏的东西 可以触摸的、
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:02.97,main screener,Demon,0,0,0,,你 不对 这位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:07.60,main screener,Demon,0,0,0,,难道是那十三灾厄中的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.55,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,滚吧 蝼蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.12,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,你可真傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:36.37,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我才刚决定 与你一起去看世界上所有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:40.89,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,但这是我唯一能够献出的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.62,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.62,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,作为替代 我需要你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:55.93,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,告诉我 世界上还存在无数精彩的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:21:00.75,main screener,Wis,0,0,0,,你的话语 伴随着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:04.84,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,嗯 毕竟是契约呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:10.27,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,那么 接下来应该去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:16.02,main screener,Marbas,0,0,0,,我第一次对计划旅行如此兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:59.26,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,然后呢 那个红发的恶魔和银发女孩一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:04.33,main screener,Lord,0,0,0,,是啊 明明很久没见过这么好的货色了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.91,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,什么叫好货色 哈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:09.27,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,停下吧 斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:14.04,main screener,Snow,0,0,0,,呐 竹波 你会让我接手这个案件的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:20.56,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,嗯 我们的任务是灭绝所有这样的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:25.32,main screener,Takenami,0,0,0,,直到所有恶魔灭绝 随你杀到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:27.65,italics screener,Snow,0,0,0,,再等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:30.50,italics screener,Snow,0,0,0,,再等一会 我就能见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:33.41,italics screener,Snow,0,0,0,,威斯媞莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:38.05,italicstop screener,Snow,0,0,0,,我一定会救出你的
